The Alex Jones Show
Sunday, 21 March 2010


[sebaygo1]




A live show today.

The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.

Today's big topic is the so-called health reform bill, which may receive a critical vote either tonight or tomorrow.

Alex also takes a number of calls.
